📄 FILE 1: theme.liquid — THE KING FILE 👑
Simple Explanation:
theme.liquid Shopify theme ki sabse powerful file hai. Yeh har page ka master wrapper hai. Jab bhi koi customer tumhara store open karta hai — chahe home page ho, product page ho, cart ho — pehle theme.liquid chalta hai, phir uske andar baaki content load hota hai.

Socho aise: TV ka frame theme.liquid hai, aur jo channel chal raha hai woh template/section hai.

