🧠 IF-THEN Logic:
IF (Yeh Karo)	THEN (Yeh Hoga)	WHY (Kyun)
theme.liquid mein font change kiya	Poori website pe font badal jayega	Har page is file se guzarta hai
theme.liquid delete kar diya	Poora store crash — kuch nahi dikhega	Shopify ko wrapper chahiye render ke liye
{{ content_for_header }} remove kiya	Analytics, Shopify scripts, cart sab band	Shopify apna zaroori code yahan inject karta hai
{{ content_for_layout }} remove kiya	Page ka content gayab — sirf header/footer dikhega	Yeh line actual template content ko call karti hai
Header-group ki line remove ki	Saari pages se header gayab ho jayega	Header yahan se render ho raha tha
Naya snippet render kiya ({% render 'xyz' %})	Har page pe woh snippet dikhega	theme.liquid = global file
CSS file ka link remove kiya	Styling toot jayegi — ugly page dikhega	Styles yahan se load ho rahi thi
JavaScript remove kiya	Interactive features band (cart, menu, search)	JS yahan se load ho raha tha
🧱 theme.liquid Ka Simplified Structure:
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="{{ request.locale.iso_code }}">
<head>
  <!-- META TAGS -->
  {% render 'meta-tags' %}
  
  <!-- CSS LOAD -->
  {% render 'stylesheets' %}
  
  <!-- FONTS LOAD -->
  {% render 'fonts' %}
  
  <!-- THEME VARIABLES (colors, spacing) -->
  {% render 'theme-styles-variables' %}
  {% render 'color-schemes' %}
  
  <!-- SHOPIFY KA APNA CODE -->
  {{ content_for_header }}
</head>

<body>
  <!-- ACCESSIBILITY -->
  {% render 'skip-to-content-link' %}
  
  <!-- HEADER (announcement + navigation) -->
  {% sections 'header-group' %}
  
  <!-- · ACTUAL PAGE CONTENT YAHAN AATA HAI · -->
  <main id="MainContent">
    {{ content_for_layout }}
  </main>
  
  <!-- FOOTER -->
  {% sections 'footer-group' %}
  
  <!-- MODALS (search, quick-add) -->
  {% render 'search-modal' %}
  {% render 'quick-add-modal' %}
  
  <!-- JAVASCRIPT LOAD -->
  {% render 'scripts' %}
  
  <!-- THEME EDITOR HELPER -->
  {% render 'theme-editor' %}
</body>
</html>
