⚠️ Common Mistakes:
✗ MISTAKE 1: content_for_header remove karna
   → Shopify analytics, checkout, cart sab toot jayega

✗ MISTAKE 2: content_for_layout remove karna
   → Page ka content hi nahi dikhega

✗ MISTAKE 3: Zyada heavy JS yahan load karna
   → Poori site slow ho jayegi (har page pe load hoga)

✗ MISTAKE 4: Inline CSS bahut zyada likhna
   → Page size badh jayega, caching ka fayda nahi milega

✓ CORRECT: Snippets use karo — code organized rahe
✓ CORRECT: Critical CSS inline, baki deferred
✓ CORRECT: JS ko defer/async se load karo
📄 FILE 2: password.liquid — THE GUARD FILE 🔒
Simple Explanation:
password.liquid ek backup layout hai jo sirf tab kaam aata hai jab store password-protected ho. Jaise theme.liquid har normal page ka wrapper hai, waise hi password.liquid sirf password page ka wrapper hai.

Socho aise: Ghar pe tala laga hai — bahar se sirf ek board dikhai de raha hai "Jaldi aa rahe hain". Woh board = password.liquid.

