│
└─── </body></html>

TOTAL CONNECTIONS: 3-5 files (bahut simple)
🧠 IF-THEN Logic:
IF (Yeh Karo)	THEN (Yeh Hoga)	WHY (Kyun)
password.liquid delete kiya	Password page ugly/broken dikhega	Shopify ko is page ka bhi layout chahiye
password.liquid mein branding add ki	Password page professional dikhega	First impression — customer launch se pehle dekhta hai
Store password enable kiya (settings mein)	theme.liquid ki jagah password.liquid use hoga	Shopify automatically switch karta hai
